diabetes: a cluster randomised controlled trial.

Gillespie P(1), O'Shea E, O'Hara MC, Dinneen SF; Irish DAFNE Study Group.

Collaborators: Dinneen SF, O'Hara MC, Daly L, O'Shea D, Smith D, McGurk C, 
