Pre-clinical functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging Part I: The kidney.

Zöllner FG(1), Kalayciyan R(2), Chacón-Caldera J(2), Zimmer F(2), Schad LR(2).

Author information:
(1)Computer Assisted Clinical Medicine, Medical Faculty Mannheim, Heidelberg 
University, Mannheim, Germany. Electronic address: 
Frank.Zoellner@medma.uni-heidelberg.de.
(2)Computer Assisted Clinical Medicine, Medical Faculty Mannheim, Heidelberg 
